**Full Year Results Announcement Summary**  

- **Net Operating Profit**: $40.8m (up 1% YoY), 15.50c per share (up 1%)  
- **Dividend per share**: 15.50c (up 2% YoY)  
- **Dividend income**: $34.7m (down 4% YoY)  
- **Option income**: $16.7m (up 1% YoY)  
- **NTA per share**: $3.40 (up from $3.36 in FY24)  
- **Share price discount to NTA**: 10.9% ($3.03 vs. $3.40 NTA)  
- **Portfolio value**: $835m; 44 holdings; 32% call option coverage  
- **Key portfolio changes**: Overweight in CSL, Macquarie Tech, ARB; underweight CBA  
- **Outlook**: Market valuation concerns; net cash position; focus on dividend yield and option income generation.  

*No capital markets actions or material structural changes identified.*
